2330static Ref<CSSValue> shapePropertyValue(const RenderStyle& style, const ShapeValue* shapeValue)
2331{
2332 if (!shapeValue)
2333 return CSSValuePool::singleton().createIdentifierValue(CSSValueNone);
2334
2335 if (shapeValue->type() == ShapeValue::Type::Box)
2336 return CSSValuePool::singleton().createValue(shapeValue->cssBox());
2337
2338 if (shapeValue->type() == ShapeValue::Type::Image) {
2339 if (shapeValue->image())
2340 return shapeValue->image()->cssValue();
2341 return CSSValuePool::singleton().createIdentifierValue(CSSValueNone);
2342 }
2343
2344 ASSERT(shapeValue->type() == ShapeValue::Type::Shape);
2345
2346 auto list = CSSValueList::createSpaceSeparated();
2347 list->append(valueForBasicShape(style, *shapeValue->shape()));
2348 if (shapeValue->cssBox() != CSSBoxType::BoxMissing)
2349 list->append(CSSValuePool::singleton().createValue(shapeValue->cssBox()));
2350 return list;
2351}
2352
2353static Ref<CSSValueList> valueForItemPositionWithOverflowAlignment(const StyleSelfAlignmentData& data)
2354{
2355 auto& cssValuePool = CSSValuePool::singleton();
2356 auto result = CSSValueList::createSpaceSeparated();
2357 if (data.positionType() == ItemPositionType::Legacy)
2358 result->append(cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueLegacy));
2359 if (data.position() == ItemPosition::Baseline)
2360 result->append(cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueBaseline));
2361 else if (data.position() == ItemPosition::LastBaseline) {
2362 result->append(cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueLast));
2363 result->append(cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueBaseline));
2364 } else {
2365 if (data.position() >= ItemPosition::Center && data.overflow() != OverflowAlignment::Default)
2366 result->append(cssValuePool.createValue(data.overflow()));
2367 if (data.position() == ItemPosition::Legacy)
2368 result->append(cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueNormal));
2369 else
2370 result->append(cssValuePool.createValue(data.position()));
2371 }
2372 ASSERT(result->length() <= 2);
2373 return result;
2374}
2375
2376static Ref<CSSValueList> valueForContentPositionAndDistributionWithOverflowAlignment(const StyleContentAlignmentData& data)
2377{
2378 auto& cssValuePool = CSSValuePool::singleton();
2379 auto result = CSSValueList::createSpaceSeparated();
2380 // Handle content-distribution values
2381 if (data.distribution() != ContentDistribution::Default)
2382 result->append(cssValuePool.createValue(data.distribution()));
2383
2384 // Handle content-position values (either as fallback or actual value)
2385 switch (data.position()) {
2386 case ContentPosition::Normal:
2387 // Handle 'normal' value, not valid as content-distribution fallback.
2388 if (data.distribution() == ContentDistribution::Default)
2389 result->append(cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueNormal));
2390 break;
2391 case ContentPosition::LastBaseline:
2392 result->append(cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueLast));
2393 result->append(cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueBaseline));
2394 break;
2395 default:
2396 // Handle overflow-alignment (only allowed for content-position values)
2397 if ((data.position() >= ContentPosition::Center || data.distribution() != ContentDistribution::Default) && data.overflow() != OverflowAlignment::Default)
2398 result->append(cssValuePool.createValue(data.overflow()));
2399 result->append(cssValuePool.createValue(data.position()));
2400 }
2401
2402 ASSERT(result->length() > 0);
2403 ASSERT(result->length() <= 3);
2404 return result;
2405}
2406
2407static Ref<CSSValue> paintOrder(PaintOrder paintOrder)
2408{
2409 if (paintOrder == PaintOrder::Normal)
2410 return CSSPrimitiveValue::createIdentifier(CSSValueNormal);
2411
2412 auto paintOrderList = CSSValueList::createSpaceSeparated();
2413 switch (paintOrder) {
2414 case PaintOrder::Normal:
2415 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
2416 break;
2417 case PaintOrder::Fill:
2418 paintOrderList->append(CSSPrimitiveValue::createIdentifier(CSSValueFill));
2419 break;
2420 case PaintOrder::FillMarkers:
2421 paintOrderList->append(CSSPrimitiveValue::createIdentifier(CSSValueFill));
2422 paintOrderList->append(CSSPrimitiveValue::createIdentifier(CSSValueMarkers));
2423 break;
2424 case PaintOrder::Stroke:
2425 paintOrderList->append(CSSPrimitiveValue::createIdentifier(CSSValueStroke));
2426 break;
2427 case PaintOrder::StrokeMarkers:
2428 paintOrderList->append(CSSPrimitiveValue::createIdentifier(CSSValueStroke));
2429 paintOrderList->append(CSSPrimitiveValue::createIdentifier(CSSValueMarkers));
2430 break;
2431 case PaintOrder::Markers:
2432 paintOrderList->append(CSSPrimitiveValue::createIdentifier(CSSValueMarkers));
2433 break;
2434 case PaintOrder::MarkersStroke:
2435 paintOrderList->append(CSSPrimitiveValue::createIdentifier(CSSValueMarkers));
2436 paintOrderList->append(CSSPrimitiveValue::createIdentifier(CSSValueStroke));
2437 break;
2438 }
2439 return paintOrderList;
2440}
2441
2442inline static bool isFlexOrGridItem(RenderObject* renderer)
2443{
2444 if (!renderer || !renderer->isBox())
2445 return false;
2446 auto& box = downcast<RenderBox>(*renderer);
2447 return box.isFlexItem() || box.isGridItem();
2448}
2449
2450RefPtr<CSSValue> ComputedStyleExtractor::customPropertyValue(const String& propertyName)
2451{
2452 Element* styledElement = this->styledElement();
2453 if (!styledElement)
2454 return nullptr;
2455
2456 if (updateStyleIfNeededForProperty(*styledElement, CSSPropertyCustom)) {
2457 // Style update may change styledElement() to PseudoElement or back.
2458 styledElement = this->styledElement();
2459 }
2460
2461 std::unique_ptr<RenderStyle> ownedStyle;
2462 auto* style = computeRenderStyleForProperty(*styledElement, m_pseudoElementSpecifier, CSSPropertyCustom, ownedStyle);
2463 if (!style)
2464 return nullptr;
2465
2466 auto* value = style->getCustomProperty(propertyName);
2467 if (!value) {
2468 auto registered = styledElement->document().getCSSRegisteredCustomPropertySet().get(propertyName);
2469 return registered ? registered->initialValueCopy() : nullptr;
2470 }
2471
2472 return WTF::switchOn(value->value(), [&](const Length& value) -> Ref<CSSValue> {
2473 return zoomAdjustedPixelValueForLength(value, *style);
2474 }, [&](auto&) -> Ref<CSSValue> {
2475 return CSSCustomPropertyValue::create(*value);
2476 });
2477}
2478
2479String ComputedStyleExtractor::customPropertyText(const String& propertyName)
2480{
2481 RefPtr<CSSValue> propertyValue = customPropertyValue(propertyName);
2482 return propertyValue ? propertyValue->cssText() : emptyString();
2483}
2484
2485static Ref<CSSFontValue> fontShorthandValueForSelectionProperties(const FontDescription& fontDescription)
2486{
2487 auto computedFont = CSSFontValue::create();
2488
2489 auto variantCaps = fontDescription.variantCaps();
2490 if (variantCaps == FontVariantCaps::Small)
2491 computedFont->variant = CSSValuePool::singleton().createIdentifierValue(CSSValueSmallCaps);
2492 else if (variantCaps == FontVariantCaps::Normal)
2493 computedFont->variant = CSSValuePool::singleton().createIdentifierValue(CSSValueNormal);
2494 else
2495 return CSSFontValue::create();
2496
2497 auto weight = fontDescription.weight();
2498 if (auto value = fontWeightKeyword(weight))
2499 computedFont->weight = CSSValuePool::singleton().createIdentifierValue(value.value());
2500 else if (isCSS21Weight(weight))
2501 computedFont->weight = CSSValuePool::singleton().createValue(static_cast<float>(weight), CSSUnitType::CSS_NUMBER);
2502 else
2503 return CSSFontValue::create();
2504
2505 if (auto keyword = fontStretchKeyword(fontDescription.stretch()))
2506 computedFont->stretch = CSSValuePool::singleton().createIdentifierValue(keyword.value());
2507 else
2508 return CSSFontValue::create();
2509
2510 if (auto italic = fontStyleKeyword(fontDescription.italic(), fontDescription.fontStyleAxis()))
2511 computedFont->style = CSSFontStyleValue::create(CSSValuePool::singleton().createIdentifierValue(italic.value()));
2512 else
2513 return CSSFontValue::create();
2514
2515 return computedFont;
2516}
2517
2518RefPtr<CSSValue> ComputedStyleExtractor::propertyValue(CSSPropertyID propertyID, EUpdateLayout updateLayout)
2519{
2520 auto* styledElement = this->styledElement();
2521 if (!styledElement)
2522 return nullptr;
2523
2524 std::unique_ptr<RenderStyle> ownedStyle;
2525 const RenderStyle* style = nullptr;
2526 RenderElement* renderer = nullptr;
2527 bool forceFullLayout = false;
2528 if (updateLayout) {
2529 Document& document = m_element->document();
2530
2531 if (updateStyleIfNeededForProperty(*styledElement, propertyID)) {
2532 // Style update may change styledElement() to PseudoElement or back.
2533 styledElement = this->styledElement();
2534 }
2535 renderer = styledRenderer();
2536
2537 if (propertyID == CSSPropertyDisplay && !renderer && is<SVGElement>(*styledElement) && !downcast<SVGElement>(*styledElement).isValid())
2538 return nullptr;
2539
2540 style = computeRenderStyleForProperty(*styledElement, m_pseudoElementSpecifier, propertyID, ownedStyle);
2541
2542 // FIXME: Some of these cases could be narrowed down or optimized better.
2543 forceFullLayout = isLayoutDependent(propertyID, style, renderer)
2544 || styledElement->isInShadowTree()
2545 || (document.styleScope().resolverIfExists() && document.styleScope().resolverIfExists()->hasViewportDependentMediaQueries() && document.ownerElement());
2546
2547 if (forceFullLayout) {
2548 document.updateLayoutIgnorePendingStylesheets();
2549 styledElement = this->styledElement();
2550 }
2551 }
2552
2553 if (!updateLayout || forceFullLayout) {
2554 style = computeRenderStyleForProperty(*styledElement, m_pseudoElementSpecifier, propertyID, ownedStyle);
2555 renderer = styledRenderer();
2556 }
2557
2558 if (!style)
2559 return nullptr;
2560
2561 return valueForPropertyInStyle(*style, propertyID, renderer);
2562}
2563
2564RefPtr<CSSValue> ComputedStyleExtractor::valueForPropertyInStyle(const RenderStyle& style, CSSPropertyID propertyID, RenderElement* renderer)
2565{
2566 auto& cssValuePool = CSSValuePool::singleton();
2567 propertyID = CSSProperty::resolveDirectionAwareProperty(propertyID, style.direction(), style.writingMode());
2568
2569 switch (propertyID) {
2570 case CSSPropertyInvalid:
2571#if ENABLE(TEXT_AUTOSIZING)
2572 case CSSPropertyInternalTextAutosizingStatus:
2573#endif
2574 break;
2575
2576 case CSSPropertyBackgroundColor:
2577 return m_allowVisitedStyle ? cssValuePool.createColorValue(style.visitedDependentColor(CSSPropertyBackgroundColor)) : currentColorOrValidColor(&style, style.backgroundColor());
2578 case CSSPropertyBackgroundImage:
2579 case CSSPropertyWebkitMaskImage: {
2580 auto& layers = propertyID == CSSPropertyWebkitMaskImage ? style.maskLayers() : style.backgroundLayers();
2581 if (!layers.next()) {
2582 if (layers.image())
2583 return layers.image()->cssValue();
2584 return cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueNone);
2585 }
2586 auto list = CSSValueList::createCommaSeparated();
2587 for (auto* currLayer = &layers; currLayer; currLayer = currLayer->next()) {
2588 if (currLayer->image())
2589 list->append(currLayer->image()->cssValue());
2590 else
2591 list->append(cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueNone));
2592 }
2593 return list;
2594 }
2595 case CSSPropertyBackgroundSize:
2596 case CSSPropertyWebkitBackgroundSize:
2597 case CSSPropertyWebkitMaskSize: {
2598 auto& layers = propertyID == CSSPropertyWebkitMaskSize ? style.maskLayers() : style.backgroundLayers();
2599 if (!layers.next())
2600 return fillSizeToCSSValue(layers.size(), style);
2601 auto list = CSSValueList::createCommaSeparated();
2602 for (auto* currLayer = &layers; currLayer; currLayer = currLayer->next())
2603 list->append(fillSizeToCSSValue(currLayer->size(), style));
2604 return list;
2605 }
2606 case CSSPropertyBackgroundRepeat:
2607 case CSSPropertyWebkitMaskRepeat: {
2608 auto& layers = propertyID == CSSPropertyWebkitMaskRepeat ? style.maskLayers() : style.backgroundLayers();
2609 if (!layers.next())
2610 return fillRepeatToCSSValue(layers.repeatX(), layers.repeatY());
2611 auto list = CSSValueList::createCommaSeparated();
2612 for (auto* currLayer = &layers; currLayer; currLayer = currLayer->next())
2613 list->append(fillRepeatToCSSValue(currLayer->repeatX(), currLayer->repeatY()));
2614 return list;
2615 }
2616 case CSSPropertyWebkitMaskSourceType: {
2617 auto& layers = style.maskLayers();
2618 if (!layers.next())
2619 return fillSourceTypeToCSSValue(layers.maskSourceType());
2620 auto list = CSSValueList::createCommaSeparated();
2621 for (auto* currLayer = &layers; currLayer; currLayer = currLayer->next())
2622 list->append(fillSourceTypeToCSSValue(currLayer->maskSourceType()));
2623 return list;
2624 }
2625 case CSSPropertyWebkitBackgroundComposite:
2626 case CSSPropertyWebkitMaskComposite: {
2627 auto& layers = propertyID == CSSPropertyWebkitMaskComposite ? style.maskLayers() : style.backgroundLayers();
2628 if (!layers.next())
2629 return cssValuePool.createValue(layers.composite());
2630 auto list = CSSValueList::createCommaSeparated();
2631 for (auto* currLayer = &layers; currLayer; currLayer = currLayer->next())
2632 list->append(cssValuePool.createValue(currLayer->composite()));
2633 return list;
2634 }
2635 case CSSPropertyBackgroundAttachment: {
2636 auto& layers = style.backgroundLayers();
2637 if (!layers.next())
2638 return cssValuePool.createValue(layers.attachment());
2639 auto list = CSSValueList::createCommaSeparated();
2640 for (auto* currLayer = &layers; currLayer; currLayer = currLayer->next())
2641 list->append(cssValuePool.createValue(currLayer->attachment()));
2642 return list;
2643 }
2644 case CSSPropertyBackgroundClip:
2645 case CSSPropertyBackgroundOrigin:
2646 case CSSPropertyWebkitBackgroundClip:
2647 case CSSPropertyWebkitBackgroundOrigin:
2648 case CSSPropertyWebkitMaskClip:
2649 case CSSPropertyWebkitMaskOrigin: {
2650 auto& layers = (propertyID == CSSPropertyWebkitMaskClip || propertyID == CSSPropertyWebkitMaskOrigin) ? style.maskLayers() : style.backgroundLayers();
2651 bool isClip = propertyID == CSSPropertyBackgroundClip || propertyID == CSSPropertyWebkitBackgroundClip || propertyID == CSSPropertyWebkitMaskClip;
2652 if (!layers.next())
2653 return cssValuePool.createValue(isClip ? layers.clip() : layers.origin());
2654 auto list = CSSValueList::createCommaSeparated();
2655 for (auto* currLayer = &layers; currLayer; currLayer = currLayer->next())
2656 list->append(cssValuePool.createValue(isClip ? currLayer->clip() : currLayer->origin()));
2657 return list;
2658 }
2659 case CSSPropertyBackgroundPosition:
2660 case CSSPropertyWebkitMaskPosition: {
2661 auto& layers = propertyID == CSSPropertyWebkitMaskPosition ? style.maskLayers() : style.backgroundLayers();
2662 if (!layers.next())
2663 return createPositionListForLayer(propertyID, layers, style);
2664
2665 auto list = CSSValueList::createCommaSeparated();
2666 for (auto* currLayer = &layers; currLayer; currLayer = currLayer->next())
2667 list->append(createPositionListForLayer(propertyID, *currLayer, style));
2668 return list;
2669 }
2670 case CSSPropertyBackgroundPositionX:
2671 case CSSPropertyWebkitMaskPositionX: {
2672 auto& layers = propertyID == CSSPropertyWebkitMaskPositionX ? style.maskLayers() : style.backgroundLayers();
2673 if (!layers.next())
2674 return cssValuePool.createValue(layers.xPosition(), style);
2675
2676 auto list = CSSValueList::createCommaSeparated();
2677 for (auto* currLayer = &layers; currLayer; currLayer = currLayer->next())
2678 list->append(cssValuePool.createValue(currLayer->xPosition(), style));
2679
2680 return list;
2681 }
2682 case CSSPropertyBackgroundPositionY:
2683 case CSSPropertyWebkitMaskPositionY: {
2684 auto& layers = propertyID == CSSPropertyWebkitMaskPositionY ? style.maskLayers() : style.backgroundLayers();
2685 if (!layers.next())
2686 return cssValuePool.createValue(layers.yPosition(), style);
2687
2688 auto list = CSSValueList::createCommaSeparated();
2689 for (auto* currLayer = &layers; currLayer; currLayer = currLayer->next())
2690 list->append(cssValuePool.createValue(currLayer->yPosition(), style));
2691
2692 return list;
2693 }
2694 case CSSPropertyBorderCollapse:
2695 if (style.borderCollapse() == BorderCollapse::Collapse)
2696 return cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueCollapse);
2697 return cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueSeparate);
2698 case CSSPropertyBorderSpacing: {
2699 auto list = CSSValueList::createSpaceSeparated();
2700 list->append(zoomAdjustedPixelValue(style.horizontalBorderSpacing(), style));
2701 list->append(zoomAdjustedPixelValue(style.verticalBorderSpacing(), style));
2702 return list;
2703 }
2704 case CSSPropertyWebkitBorderHorizontalSpacing:
2705 return zoomAdjustedPixelValue(style.horizontalBorderSpacing(), style);
2706 case CSSPropertyWebkitBorderVerticalSpacing:
2707 return zoomAdjustedPixelValue(style.verticalBorderSpacing(), style);
2708 case CSSPropertyBorderImageSource:
2709 if (style.borderImageSource())
2710 return style.borderImageSource()->cssValue();
2711 return cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueNone);
2712 case CSSPropertyBorderTopColor:
2713 return m_allowVisitedStyle ? cssValuePool.createColorValue(style.visitedDependentColor(CSSPropertyBorderTopColor)) : currentColorOrValidColor(&style, style.borderTopColor());
2714 case CSSPropertyBorderRightColor:
2715 return m_allowVisitedStyle ? cssValuePool.createColorValue(style.visitedDependentColor(CSSPropertyBorderRightColor)) : currentColorOrValidColor(&style, style.borderRightColor());
2716 case CSSPropertyBorderBottomColor:
2717 return m_allowVisitedStyle ? cssValuePool.createColorValue(style.visitedDependentColor(CSSPropertyBorderBottomColor)) : currentColorOrValidColor(&style, style.borderBottomColor());
2718 case CSSPropertyBorderLeftColor:
2719 return m_allowVisitedStyle ? cssValuePool.createColorValue(style.visitedDependentColor(CSSPropertyBorderLeftColor)) : currentColorOrValidColor(&style, style.borderLeftColor());
2720 case CSSPropertyBorderTopStyle:
2721 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.borderTopStyle());
2722 case CSSPropertyBorderRightStyle:
2723 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.borderRightStyle());
2724 case CSSPropertyBorderBottomStyle:
2725 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.borderBottomStyle());
2726 case CSSPropertyBorderLeftStyle:
2727 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.borderLeftStyle());
2728 case CSSPropertyBorderTopWidth:
2729 return zoomAdjustedPixelValue(style.borderTopWidth(), style);
2730 case CSSPropertyBorderRightWidth:
2731 return zoomAdjustedPixelValue(style.borderRightWidth(), style);
2732 case CSSPropertyBorderBottomWidth:
2733 return zoomAdjustedPixelValue(style.borderBottomWidth(), style);
2734 case CSSPropertyBorderLeftWidth:
2735 return zoomAdjustedPixelValue(style.borderLeftWidth(), style);
2736 case CSSPropertyBottom:
2737 return positionOffsetValue(style, CSSPropertyBottom, renderer);
2738 case CSSPropertyWebkitBoxAlign:
2739 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.boxAlign());
2740#if ENABLE(CSS_BOX_DECORATION_BREAK)
2741 case CSSPropertyWebkitBoxDecorationBreak:
2742 if (style.boxDecorationBreak() == BoxDecorationBreak::Slice)
2743 return cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueSlice);
2744 return cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueClone);
2745#endif
2746 case CSSPropertyWebkitBoxDirection:
2747 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.boxDirection());
2748 case CSSPropertyWebkitBoxFlex:
2749 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.boxFlex(), CSSUnitType::CSS_NUMBER);
2750 case CSSPropertyWebkitBoxFlexGroup:
2751 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.boxFlexGroup(), CSSUnitType::CSS_NUMBER);
2752 case CSSPropertyWebkitBoxLines:
2753 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.boxLines());
2754 case CSSPropertyWebkitBoxOrdinalGroup:
2755 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.boxOrdinalGroup(), CSSUnitType::CSS_NUMBER);
2756 case CSSPropertyWebkitBoxOrient:
2757 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.boxOrient());
2758 case CSSPropertyWebkitBoxPack:
2759 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.boxPack());
2760 case CSSPropertyWebkitBoxReflect:
2761 return valueForReflection(style.boxReflect(), style);
2762 case CSSPropertyBoxShadow:
2763 case CSSPropertyWebkitBoxShadow:
2764 return valueForShadow(style.boxShadow(), propertyID, style);
2765 case CSSPropertyCaptionSide:
2766 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.captionSide());
2767 case CSSPropertyCaretColor:
2768 return m_allowVisitedStyle ? cssValuePool.createColorValue(style.visitedDependentColor(CSSPropertyCaretColor)) : currentColorOrValidColor(&style, style.caretColor());
2769 case CSSPropertyClear:
2770 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.clear());
2771 case CSSPropertyColor:
2772 return cssValuePool.createColorValue(m_allowVisitedStyle ? style.visitedDependentColor(CSSPropertyColor) : style.color());
2773 case CSSPropertyWebkitPrintColorAdjust:
2774 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.printColorAdjust());
2775 case CSSPropertyWebkitColumnAxis:
2776 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.columnAxis());
2777 case CSSPropertyColumnCount:
2778 if (style.hasAutoColumnCount())
2779 return cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueAuto);
2780 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.columnCount(), CSSUnitType::CSS_NUMBER);
2781 case CSSPropertyColumnFill:
2782 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.columnFill());
2783 case CSSPropertyColumnGap:
2784 if (style.columnGap().isNormal())
2785 return cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueNormal);
2786 return zoomAdjustedPixelValueForLength(style.columnGap().length(), style);
2787 case CSSPropertyRowGap:
2788 if (style.rowGap().isNormal())
2789 return cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueNormal);
2790 return zoomAdjustedPixelValueForLength(style.rowGap().length(), style);
2791 case CSSPropertyWebkitColumnProgression:
2792 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.columnProgression());
2793 case CSSPropertyColumnRuleColor:
2794 return m_allowVisitedStyle ? cssValuePool.createColorValue(style.visitedDependentColor(CSSPropertyOutlineColor)) : currentColorOrValidColor(&style, style.columnRuleColor());
2795 case CSSPropertyColumnRuleStyle:
2796 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.columnRuleStyle());
2797 case CSSPropertyColumnRuleWidth:
2798 return zoomAdjustedPixelValue(style.columnRuleWidth(), style);
2799 case CSSPropertyColumnSpan:
2800 return cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(style.columnSpan() == ColumnSpan::All ? CSSValueAll : CSSValueNone);
2801 case CSSPropertyWebkitColumnBreakAfter:
2802 return cssValuePool.createValue(convertToColumnBreak(style.breakAfter()));
2803 case CSSPropertyWebkitColumnBreakBefore:
2804 return cssValuePool.createValue(convertToColumnBreak(style.breakBefore()));
2805 case CSSPropertyWebkitColumnBreakInside:
2806 return cssValuePool.createValue(convertToColumnBreak(style.breakInside()));
2807 case CSSPropertyColumnWidth:
2808 if (style.hasAutoColumnWidth())
2809 return cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueAuto);
2810 return zoomAdjustedPixelValue(style.columnWidth(), style);
2811 case CSSPropertyTabSize:
2812 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.tabSize().widthInPixels(1.0), style.tabSize().isSpaces() ? CSSUnitType::CSS_NUMBER : CSSUnitType::CSS_PX);
2813 case CSSPropertyCursor: {
2814 RefPtr<CSSValueList> list;
2815 auto* cursors = style.cursors();
2816 if (cursors && cursors->size() > 0) {
2817 list = CSSValueList::createCommaSeparated();
2818 for (unsigned i = 0; i < cursors->size(); ++i)
2819 if (StyleImage* image = cursors->at(i).image())
2820 list->append(image->cssValue());
2821 }
2822 auto value = cssValuePool.createValue(style.cursor());
2823 if (list) {
2824 list->append(WTFMove(value));
2825 return list;
2826 }
2827 return value;
2828 }
2829#if ENABLE(CURSOR_VISIBILITY)
2830 case CSSPropertyWebkitCursorVisibility:
2831 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.cursorVisibility());
2832#endif
2833 case CSSPropertyDirection:
2834 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.direction());
2835 case CSSPropertyDisplay:
2836 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.display());
2837 case CSSPropertyEmptyCells:
2838 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.emptyCells());
2839 case CSSPropertyAlignContent:
2840 return valueForContentPositionAndDistributionWithOverflowAlignment(style.alignContent());
2841 case CSSPropertyAlignItems:
2842 return valueForItemPositionWithOverflowAlignment(style.alignItems());
2843 case CSSPropertyAlignSelf:
2844 return valueForItemPositionWithOverflowAlignment(style.alignSelf());
2845 case CSSPropertyFlex:
2846 return getCSSPropertyValuesForShorthandProperties(flexShorthand());
2847 case CSSPropertyFlexBasis:
2848 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.flexBasis(), style);
2849 case CSSPropertyFlexDirection:
2850 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.flexDirection());
2851 case CSSPropertyFlexFlow:
2852 return getCSSPropertyValuesForShorthandProperties(flexFlowShorthand());
2853 case CSSPropertyFlexGrow:
2854 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.flexGrow());
2855 case CSSPropertyFlexShrink:
2856 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.flexShrink());
2857 case CSSPropertyFlexWrap:
2858 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.flexWrap());
2859 case CSSPropertyJustifyContent:
2860 return valueForContentPositionAndDistributionWithOverflowAlignment(style.justifyContent());
2861 case CSSPropertyJustifyItems:
2862 return valueForItemPositionWithOverflowAlignment(style.justifyItems());
2863 case CSSPropertyJustifySelf:
2864 return valueForItemPositionWithOverflowAlignment(style.justifySelf());
2865 case CSSPropertyPlaceContent:
2866 return getCSSPropertyValuesForShorthandProperties(placeContentShorthand());
2867 case CSSPropertyPlaceItems:
2868 return getCSSPropertyValuesForShorthandProperties(placeItemsShorthand());
2869 case CSSPropertyPlaceSelf:
2870 return getCSSPropertyValuesForShorthandProperties(placeSelfShorthand());
2871 case CSSPropertyOrder:
2872 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.order(), CSSUnitType::CSS_NUMBER);
2873 case CSSPropertyFloat:
2874 if (style.display() != DisplayType::None && style.hasOutOfFlowPosition())
2875 return cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueNone);
2876 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.floating());
2877 case CSSPropertyFont: {
2878 auto computedFont = fontShorthandValueForSelectionProperties(style.fontDescription());
2879 computedFont->size = fontSizeFromStyle(style);
2880 computedFont->lineHeight = lineHeightFromStyle(style);
2881 computedFont->family = fontFamilyListFromStyle(style);
2882 return computedFont;
2883 }
2884 case CSSPropertyFontFamily:
2885 return fontFamilyFromStyle(style);
2886 case CSSPropertyFontSize:
2887 return fontSizeFromStyle(style);
2888 case CSSPropertyFontStyle:
2889 return fontStyleFromStyle(style);
2890 case CSSPropertyFontStretch:
2891 return fontStretchFromStyle(style);
2892 case CSSPropertyFontVariant:
2893 return fontVariantFromStyle(style);
2894 case CSSPropertyFontWeight:
2895 return fontWeightFromStyle(style);
2896 case CSSPropertyFontSynthesis:
2897 return fontSynthesisFromStyle(style);
2898 case CSSPropertyFontFeatureSettings: {
2899 const FontFeatureSettings& featureSettings = style.fontDescription().featureSettings();
2900 if (!featureSettings.size())
2901 return cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueNormal);
2902 auto list = CSSValueList::createCommaSeparated();
2903 for (auto& feature : featureSettings)
2904 list->append(CSSFontFeatureValue::create(FontTag(feature.tag()), feature.value()));
2905 return list;
2906 }
2907#if ENABLE(VARIATION_FONTS)
2908 case CSSPropertyFontVariationSettings: {
2909 const FontVariationSettings& variationSettings = style.fontDescription().variationSettings();
2910 if (variationSettings.isEmpty())
2911 return cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueNormal);
2912 auto list = CSSValueList::createCommaSeparated();
2913 for (auto& feature : variationSettings)
2914 list->append(CSSFontVariationValue::create(feature.tag(), feature.value()));
2915 return list;
2916 }
2917 case CSSPropertyFontOpticalSizing:
2918 return cssValuePool.createValue(style.fontDescription().opticalSizing());
2919#endif
2920 case CSSPropertyGridAutoFlow: {
2921 auto list = CSSValueList::createSpaceSeparated();
2922 ASSERT(style.isGridAutoFlowDirectionRow() || style.isGridAutoFlowDirectionColumn());
2923 if (style.isGridAutoFlowDirectionRow())
2924 list->append(cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueRow));
2925 else
2926 list->append(cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueColumn));
2927
2928 if (style.isGridAutoFlowAlgorithmDense())
2929 list->append(cssValuePool.createIdentifierValue(CSSValueDense));
2930
2931 return list;
2932 }
2933
2934 // Specs mention that getComputedStyle() should return the used value of the property instead of the computed
2935 // one for grid-template-{rows|columns} but not for the grid-auto-{rows|columns} as things like
2936 // grid-auto-columns: 2fr; cannot be resolved to a value in pixels as the '2fr' means very different things
2937 // depending on the size of the explicit grid or the number of implicit tracks added to the grid. See
2938 // http://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/www-style/2013Nov/0014.html
2939 case CSSPropertyGridAutoColumns:
2940 return valueForGridTrackSizeList(ForColumns, style);
2941 case CSSPropertyGridAutoRows:
2942 return valueForGridTrackSizeList(ForRows, style);
2943
2944 case CSSPropertyGridTemplateColumns:
2945 return valueForGridTrackList(ForColumns, renderer, style);
2946 case CSSPropertyGridTemplateRows:
2947 return valueForGridTrackList(ForRows, renderer, style);
2948
2949 case CSSPropertyGridColumnStart:
2950 return valueForGridPosition(style.gridItemColumnStart());
2951 case CSSPropertyGridColumnEnd:
2952 return valueForGridPosition(style.gridItemColumnEnd());
2953 case CSSPropertyGridRowStart:
2954 return valueForGridPosition(style.gridItemRowStart());
2955 case CSSPropertyGridRowEnd:

4053 case CSSPropertyMarkerStart:
4054 case CSSPropertyMaskType:
4055 case CSSPropertyShapeRendering:
4056 case CSSPropertyStroke:
4057 case CSSPropertyStrokeDasharray:
4058 case CSSPropertyStrokeOpacity:
4059 case CSSPropertyAlignmentBaseline:
4060 case CSSPropertyBaselineShift:
4061 case CSSPropertyDominantBaseline:
4062 case CSSPropertyGlyphOrientationHorizontal:
4063 case CSSPropertyGlyphOrientationVertical:
4064 case CSSPropertyKerning:
4065 case CSSPropertyTextAnchor:
4066 case CSSPropertyVectorEffect:
4067 return svgPropertyValue(propertyID);
4068 case CSSPropertyCustom:
4069 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
4070 return nullptr;
4071 }
4072
4073 return nullptr;
4074}

4076String CSSComputedStyleDeclaration::getPropertyValue(CSSPropertyID propertyID) const
4077{
4078 auto value = getPropertyCSSValue(propertyID);
4079 if (!value)
4080 return emptyString(); // FIXME: Should this be null instead, as it is in StyleProperties::getPropertyValue?
4081 return value->cssText();

4084unsigned CSSComputedStyleDeclaration::length() const
4085{
4086 updateStyleIfNeededForProperty(m_element.get(), CSSPropertyCustom);
4087
4088 auto* style = m_element->computedStyle(m_pseudoElementSpecifier);
4089 if (!style)
4090 return 0;
4091
4092 return numComputedPropertyIDs + style->inheritedCustomProperties().size() + style->nonInheritedCustomProperties().size();
4093}
4094
4095String CSSComputedStyleDeclaration::item(unsigned i) const
4096{
4097 if (i >= length())
4098 return String();
4099
4100 if (i < numComputedPropertyIDs)
4101 return getPropertyNameString(computedPropertyIDs[i]);
4102
4103 auto* style = m_element->computedStyle(m_pseudoElementSpecifier);
4104 if (!style)
4105 return String();
4106
4107 const auto& inheritedCustomProperties = style->inheritedCustomProperties();
4108
4109 if (i < numComputedPropertyIDs + inheritedCustomProperties.size()) {
4110 auto results = copyToVector(inheritedCustomProperties.keys());
4111 return results.at(i - numComputedPropertyIDs);
4112 }
4113
4114 const auto& nonInheritedCustomProperties = style->nonInheritedCustomProperties();
4115 auto results = copyToVector(nonInheritedCustomProperties.keys());
4116 return results.at(i - inheritedCustomProperties.size() - numComputedPropertyIDs);
4117}
4118
4119bool ComputedStyleExtractor::propertyMatches(CSSPropertyID propertyID, const CSSValue* value)
4120{
4121 if (!m_element)
4122 return false;
4123 if (propertyID == CSSPropertyFontSize && is<CSSPrimitiveValue>(*value)) {
4124 m_element->document().updateLayoutIgnorePendingStylesheets();
4125 if (auto* style = m_element->computedStyle(m_pseudoElementSpecifier)) {
4126 if (CSSValueID sizeIdentifier = style->fontDescription().keywordSizeAsIdentifier()) {
4127 auto& primitiveValue = downcast<CSSPrimitiveValue>(*value);
4128 if (primitiveValue.isValueID() && primitiveValue.valueID() == sizeIdentifier)
4129 return true;
4130 }
4131 }
4132 }
4133 RefPtr<CSSValue> computedValue = propertyValue(propertyID);
4134 return computedValue && value && computedValue->equals(*value);
4135}

4145RefPtr<CSSValueList> ComputedStyleExtractor::getCSSPropertyValuesFor2SidesShorthand(const StylePropertyShorthand& shorthand)
4146{
4147 auto list = CSSValueList::createSpaceSeparated();
4148
4149 // Assume the properties are in the usual order start, end.
4150 auto startValue = propertyValue(shorthand.properties()[0], DoNotUpdateLayout);
4151 auto endValue = propertyValue(shorthand.properties()[1], DoNotUpdateLayout);
4152
4153 // All 2 properties must be specified.
4154 if (!startValue || !endValue)
4155 return nullptr;
4156
4157 bool showEnd = !compareCSSValuePtr(startValue, endValue);
4158
4159 list->append(startValue.releaseNonNull());
4160 if (showEnd)
4161 list->append(endValue.releaseNonNull());
4162
4163 return list;
4164}
4165
4166RefPtr<CSSValueList> ComputedStyleExtractor::getCSSPropertyValuesFor4SidesShorthand(const StylePropertyShorthand& shorthand)
4167{
4168 auto list = CSSValueList::createSpaceSeparated();
4169
4170 // Assume the properties are in the usual order top, right, bottom, left.
4171 auto topValue = propertyValue(shorthand.properties()[0], DoNotUpdateLayout);
4172 auto rightValue = propertyValue(shorthand.properties()[1], DoNotUpdateLayout);
4173 auto bottomValue = propertyValue(shorthand.properties()[2], DoNotUpdateLayout);
4174 auto leftValue = propertyValue(shorthand.properties()[3], DoNotUpdateLayout);
4175
4176 // All 4 properties must be specified.
4177 if (!topValue || !rightValue || !bottomValue || !leftValue)
4178 return nullptr;
4179
4180 bool showLeft = !compareCSSValuePtr(rightValue, leftValue);
4181 bool showBottom = !compareCSSValuePtr(topValue, bottomValue) || showLeft;
4182 bool showRight = !compareCSSValuePtr(topValue, rightValue) || showBottom;
4183
4184 list->append(topValue.releaseNonNull());
4185 if (showRight)
4186 list->append(rightValue.releaseNonNull());
4187 if (showBottom)
4188 list->append(bottomValue.releaseNonNull());
4189 if (showLeft)
4190 list->append(leftValue.releaseNonNull());
4191
4192 return list;
4193}

4203Ref<MutableStyleProperties> ComputedStyleExtractor::copyPropertiesInSet(const CSSPropertyID* set, unsigned length)
4204{
4205 Vector<CSSProperty> list;
4206 list.reserveInitialCapacity(length);
4207 for (unsigned i = 0; i < length; ++i) {
4208 if (auto value = propertyValue(set[i]))
4209 list.append(CSSProperty(set[i], WTFMove(value), false));
4210 }
4211 return MutableStyleProperties::create(WTFMove(list));
4212}
4213
4214Ref<MutableStyleProperties> ComputedStyleExtractor::copyProperties()
4215{
4216 Vector<CSSProperty> list;
4217 list.reserveInitialCapacity(numCSSProperties);
4218 for (unsigned i = firstCSSProperty; i < lastCSSProperty; ++i) {
4219 auto propertyID = convertToCSSPropertyID(i);
4220 if (auto value = propertyValue(propertyID))
4221 list.append(CSSProperty(propertyID, WTFMove(value)));
4222 }
4223 return MutableStyleProperties::create(WTFMove(list));
4224}

4231RefPtr<DeprecatedCSSOMValue> CSSComputedStyleDeclaration::getPropertyCSSValue(const String& propertyName)
4232{
4233 if (isCustomPropertyName(propertyName)) {
4234 auto value = ComputedStyleExtractor(m_element.ptr(), m_allowVisitedStyle, m_pseudoElementSpecifier).customPropertyValue(propertyName);
4235 if (!value)
4236 return nullptr;

4238 }

4241 if (!propertyID)

4244 if (!value)

4246 return value->createDeprecatedCSSOMWrapper(*this);

4301Ref<CSSValueList> ComputedStyleExtractor::getBackgroundShorthandValue()
4302{
4303 static const CSSPropertyID propertiesBeforeSlashSeperator[5] = { CSSPropertyBackgroundColor, CSSPropertyBackgroundImage, CSSPropertyBackgroundRepeat, CSSPropertyBackgroundAttachment, CSSPropertyBackgroundPosition };
4304 static const CSSPropertyID propertiesAfterSlashSeperator[3] = { CSSPropertyBackgroundSize, CSSPropertyBackgroundOrigin, CSSPropertyBackgroundClip };
4305
4306 auto list = CSSValueList::createSlashSeparated();
4307 list->append(getCSSPropertyValuesForShorthandProperties(StylePropertyShorthand(CSSPropertyBackground, propertiesBeforeSlashSeperator)));
4308 list->append(getCSSPropertyValuesForShorthandProperties(StylePropertyShorthand(CSSPropertyBackground, propertiesAfterSlashSeperator)));
4309 return list;
4310}
